/07e7/05/04/1110093195_0:160:3072:1888_640x0_80_0_0_a6d8e39c56651bf91cd41787d2b41ffc.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/04/1110093195_0:160:3072:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_3d01c5c62112321e6e51a4acdd3eb5ec.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/04/1110093195_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_3bac04b6ec667cfa8d811605e5098dfc.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / 亚历克斯·埃德尔曼</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据华盛顿（人造卫星）网报道：美国司法部在周五的新闻稿中称，华盛顿大都会警察局（MPD）中尉肖恩·拉蒙德被指控向保守派组织“骄傲男孩”的领导人恩里克·塔里奥泄露信息。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “根据起诉书，拉蒙德担任 MPD 国土安全局情报处的主管。从 2019 年 7 月开始至少持续到 2021 年 1 月，拉蒙德和塔里奥就骄傲男孩计划在哥伦比亚特区开展的活动保持定期联系，”司法部在一份新闻稿中说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">起诉书称，至少早在 2020 年 7 月，拉蒙德就开始使用 Telegram 向塔里奥提供与骄傲男孩在华盛顿的活动有关的执法活动信息。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>新闻稿称，拉蒙德向塔里奥传递了与警方调查 2020 年 12 月 12 日焚烧“黑人的命也是命”横幅事件有关的机密执法信息。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">新闻稿称，当局于 2021 年 1 月对塔里奥发出了逮捕令，当时拉蒙德通过电报通知他逮捕令已经签署。该新闻稿称，两人定期联系，协调骄傲男孩计划在 2019 年 7 月至 2021 年 1 月期间在华盛顿举行的活动。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>司法部还在新闻稿中表示，拉蒙德通过向联邦调查人员作出虚假和误导性陈述来阻挠调查。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">预计拉蒙德将于周五晚些时候在美国哥伦比亚特区地方法院被传讯。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">新闻稿称，妨碍司法罪的法定最高刑期为 30 年，而作出虚假陈述的单一指控可能意味着法定最高刑期为五年。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 19 May 2023 22:52:55 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/us-cop-charged-for-leaking-police-information-to-proud-boys-leader-1110472583.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/us-cop-charged-for-leaking-police-information-to-proud-boys-leader-1110472583.html<category>美洲</category><category>司法部</category><category>警视厅</category><category>哥伦比亚特区</category><category>华盛顿</category><category>电报</category><category>骄傲的男孩</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[North Korea: Joint US-South Korean Drills Put Region on 'Brink of Explosion']]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110470544" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/106119/07/1061190717_0:0:4000:2348_1440x900_80_0_1_7903990ccfc71e05329c88cbf57f7722.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1061190716" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/north-korea-joint-us-south-korean-drills-put-region-on-brink-of-explosion-1110470544.html?share-img=1061190716"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Ahn Young-joon /</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">美国陆军的阿帕奇​​直升机（文件）</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="A U.S. Army's Apache helicopter (File) - Sputnik International, 1920, 19.05.2023" title="美国陆军的阿帕奇​​直升机（文件）" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/106119/07/1061190717_0:98:4001:2348_1920x0_80_0_0_fcc12023e4bb65a13d2cd01514e51e97.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/106119/07/1061190717_0:98:4001:2348_640x0_80_0_0_171fbec47a94af58460318e692569d9c.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/106119/07/1061190717_0:98:4001:2348_1280x0_80_0_0_c54b14e19893457cbd8056196c94e594.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/106119/07/1061190717_0:98:4001:2348_1920x0_80_0_0_fcc12023e4bb65a13d2cd01514e51e97.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © AP Photo / Ahn Young-joon / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊恩德马蒂诺</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_demartino_ian/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">韩国局势近期升温，韩美多次在该地区进行军事演习。朝鲜以导弹试验和演示作为回应，他们的武器不仅可以打到首尔，还可以打到日本和其他地区。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">朝鲜周五警告说，韩国和美国之间的联合军事演习正在使该地区接近武装冲突。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">朝鲜官方媒体发表的一篇文章称，半岛“处于爆炸的边缘”，联合军事演习“变得更加不加掩饰和危险[本质上]”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p>该媒体还表示，“[一次]‘歼灭’核电的演习纯粹是胡说八道。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110470544" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/north-korea-joint-us-south-korean-drills-put-region-on-brink-of-explosion-1110470544.html?share-block=1110470547" data-title="The outlet also said that “[an] exercise for ‘annihilating’ a nuclear power is just sheer bulls**t.”"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">韩国和美国将开始有史以来最大规模的军事演习，从 5 月 25 日到 6 月 15 日分五个阶段进行。它将涉及空中、海上和陆地部队，包括 F-35A 战斗机、AH- 64-Apache 直升机、各种坦克和多管火箭发射器。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>它还将纪念韩美同盟70周年和韩国建军75周年。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">朝鲜这篇题为“<strong>无休止的战争行动没有尽头”的文章称，</strong> “主权国家拥有为自己配备更强大的自卫手段以应对当前严峻形势和潜在威胁的合法权利。 ” </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “美国和南朝鲜傀儡战争贩子的疯狂核战争举动将招致相应的反制，”它继续警告说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110470544" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/north-korea-joint-us-south-korean-drills-put-region-on-brink-of-explosion-1110470544.html?share-block=1110470701" data-title="“The frantic nuclear war moves of the United States and the south Korean puppet warmongers will invite corresponding counteraction,&amp;quot; it goes on to warn."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 4 月，白宫宣布了《华盛顿宣言》，这是韩国和美国就“核威慑”达成的协议，文章称其为“对朝鲜 [朝鲜民主主义人民共和国] 的核威胁和勒索。” ”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国坚称其军事演习无意挑衅朝鲜，而是旨在表明其保护其盟友免受朝鲜潜在袭击的承诺。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 19 May 2023 21:27:54 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/north-korea-joint-us-south-korean-drills-put-region-on-brink-of-explosion-1110470544.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/north-korea-joint-us-south-korean-drills-put-region-on-brink-of-explosion-1110470544.html<category>亚洲</category><category>韩国</category><category>朝鲜</category><category>F-35A</category><category>汉城</category><category>日本</category><category>白色的房子</category><category>北朝鲜</category><category>军事演习</category><category>华盛顿</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Pentagon ‘No Longer Confident’ Syria Drone Strike Killed Al-Qaeda Leader Instead of Farmer]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110470246" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107265/88/1072658817_0:0:1280:850_1440x900_80_0_1_035c342c6aa9cbaa9ba30bd458283344.jpg?source-sid=not_sputnik_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1072658816" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/pentagon-no-longer-confident-syria-drone-strike-killed-al-qaeda-leader-instead-of-farmer-1110470246.html?share-img=1072658816"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© 照片： <a href="http://www.afrc.af.mil/shared/media/photodb/photos/090127-F-7383P-002.JPG" title="美国空军照片 / Lt. Col. Leslie Pratt">美国空军照片 / Lt. Col. Leslie Pratt</a> /</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">MQ-9 Reaper 无人机</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="An MQ-9 Reaper unmanned aerial vehicle - Sputnik International, 1920, 19.05.2023" title="MQ-9 死神无人机" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107265/88/1072658817_0:130:1280:850_1920x0_80_0_0_8e18b36486ffc12e87e96811ea4dd80e.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107265/88/1072658817_0:130:1280:850_640x0_80_0_0_668668f9a2a578a126275f6dccc4e889.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107265/88/1072658817_0:130:1280:850_1280x0_80_0_0_d4049dc3c7d96e6ebf04f9096c8ecd12.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107265/88/1072658817_0:130:1280:850_1920x0_80_0_0_8e18b36486ffc12e87e96811ea4dd80e.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 照片： <a href="http://www.afrc.af.mil/shared/media/photodb/photos/090127-F-7383P-002.JPG" title="美国空军照片 / Lt. Col. Leslie Pratt">美国空军照片 / Lt. Col. Leslie Pratt</a> / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">芳汀嘉迪尼耶</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_gardinier_fantine/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">尽管自 2014 年以来就声称要在叙利亚打击伊斯兰国*和其他恐怖组织，但美军从未获得叙利亚政府的许可在该地区开展行动。此外，美军打着支持库尔德盟军的幌子，继续帮助占领该国东部三分之一的领土。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">五角大楼此前曾声称 5 月 3 日在叙利亚西北部发动的一次空袭打死了一名基地组织**领导人，但现在却表示怀疑。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “我们不再相信我们杀死了一名高级空军基地官员，”美国国防部一名高级官员周五告诉华盛顿特区一家报纸。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110470246" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/pentagon-no-longer-confident-syria-drone-strike-killed-al-qaeda-leader-instead-of-farmer-1110470246.html?share-block=1110470248" data-title="“We are no longer confident we killed a senior AQ official,” a senior US Department of Defense official told a Washington, DC, newspaper on Friday."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">然而，同一份报纸报道说，五角大楼的其他官员仍然坚称他们杀死了恐怖组织的一名成员。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">袭击于 5 月 3 日在伊德利卜省北部的 Qorqanya 镇附近进行，该地区仍被与基地组织结盟的民兵和土耳其军队占领。美国中央司令部声称，它使用“地狱火”导弹杀死了“基地组织的一名高级领导人”。然而，受害者的家人很快认出他是 Lotfi Hassan Misto，一名 56 岁的牧羊人和前瓦工，与基地组织没有任何关系。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “他与革命无关。 ......他与 Al-Nusra 阵线或伊斯兰国没有任何关系“或任何其他恐怖组织，Lotfi 的兄弟穆罕默德告诉记者。 Al-Nusra 曾是基地组织的前线组织，该组织于 2017 年与其他类似组织合并成立了 Hay&#39;at Tahrir al-Sham (HTS)。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110470246" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/pentagon-no-longer-confident-syria-drone-strike-killed-al-qaeda-leader-instead-of-farmer-1110470246.html?share-block=1110470251" data-title="“He had nothing to do with the revolution. ... He had nothing to do with the Al-Nusra Front or with the Islamic State” or any other terrorist group, Lotfi’s brother, Mohamed, told reporters. Al-Nusra was a former front group for Al-Qaeda that merged with other similar groups to form Hay’at Tahrir al-Sham (HTS) in 2017."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">米斯托的故事传开后，五角大楼于 5 月 9 日表示，“正在确认袭击中遇难者的身份”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这远不是美国第一次犯这样的错误。 2021 年 8 月，在<u><a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20220829/we-believed-kabul-would-fall-former-centcom-chief-says-us-brass-long-opposed-afghanistan-pullout-1100133828.html" target="_blank">美国从阿富汗撤军</a></u>的最后几天，美国在喀布尔市内发动空袭，据称杀死了一名正在前往该市主要机场外集结的平民的 Daesh-Khorasan 自杀式炸弹袭击者。然而，几周后， <u><a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20210917/us-gen-mckenzie-admits-kabul-airstrike-was-a-mistake-killed-on-afghan-civilians-1089168945.html" target="_blank">中央司令部承认</a></u>，空袭导致一家美国援助组织的雇员泽马里·艾哈迈迪 (Zemari Ahmadi) 和他的其他九名家庭成员丧生，其中包括七名儿童。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <em>*Daesh（也称为 ISIS/ISIL/IS）是一个在俄罗斯和许多其他国家被取缔的恐怖组织。</em></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <em>**基地组织和努斯拉阵线 (Hay&#39;at Tahrir al-Sham) 是俄罗斯和许多其他国家/地区禁止的恐怖组织。</em></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 19 May 2023 21:15:23 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/pentagon-no-longer-confident-syria-drone-strike-killed-al-qaeda-leader-instead-of-farmer-1110470246.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/pentagon-no-longer-confident-syria-drone-strike-killed-al-qaeda-leader-instead-of-farmer-1110470246.html<category>世界</category><category>叙利亚</category><category>解放沙姆</category><category>空袭</category><category>平民死亡</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Republicans ‘Press Pause’ on Debt Ceiling Talks as June 1 Default Deadline Looms]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110469706" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/10/1110397042_0:0:3055:2037_1440x900_80_0_1_be4b1f2dd09cb9835784cdba828bceef.jpg?source-sid=afp" data-photoview-image-id="1110397024" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/republicans-press-pause-on-debt-ceiling-talks-as-june-1-default-deadline-looms-1110469706.html?share-img=1110397024"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / SAUL LOEB</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">3 月 17 日，美国总统乔·拜登在加利福尼亚州共和党众议院议长凯文·麦卡锡的陪同下，于圣帕特里克节一年一度的爱尔兰之友午餐会后离开华盛顿特区的美国国会大厦， 2023年</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="afp" alt="US President Joe Biden, accompanied by Speaker of the House Kevin McCarthy, Republican of California, departs after the annual Friends of Ireland luncheon on St. Patrick's Day at the US Capitol in Washington, DC, on March 17, 2023 - Sputnik International, 1920, 19.05.2023" title="2023 年 3 月 17 日，美国总统乔·拜登在加利福尼亚州共和党众议院议长凯文·麦卡锡的陪同下，在圣帕特里克节一年一度的爱尔兰之友午餐会后离开华盛顿特区的美国国会大厦" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/10/1110397042_0:160:3055:1878_1920x0_80_0_0_2df9847e7913bbfd9671274eea1ff55f.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/10/1110397042_0:160:3055:1878_640x0_80_0_0_0ef54892a0a2c661ed7af1586d999ff0.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/10/1110397042_0:160:3055:1878_1280x0_80_0_0_89209a56b5c316e66f3b9a8fc45df945.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/10/1110397042_0:160:3055:1878_1920x0_80_0_0_2df9847e7913bbfd9671274eea1ff55f.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / SAUL LOEB </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">芳汀嘉迪尼耶</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_gardinier_fantine/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">如果联邦政府无法拨出新的资金来偿还债务，它将违约，进一步损害其信用评级并引发经济危机。财政部警告说，违约最早可能在 6 月 1 日发生。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">周五，民主党控制的白宫和共和党控制的美国众议院之间的最新一轮谈判破裂，据报道共和党议员走出房间以示抗议。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “除非人们愿意就如何真正向前迈进并做正确的事情进行合理的对话，否则我们不会坐在这里自言自语，”众议员加勒特格雷夫斯 (R-LA) 告诉记者。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110469706" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/republicans-press-pause-on-debt-ceiling-talks-as-june-1-default-deadline-looms-1110469706.html?share-block=1110469708" data-title="“Until people are willing to have reasonable conversations about how you can actually move forward and do the right thing, then we’re not gonna sit here and talk to ourselves,” Rep. Garret Graves (R-LA) told reporters."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “我们决定暂停，因为它只是没有成效，”他补充说，并指出他不确定谈判是否会在周末恢复。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">由于共和党在众议院占多数，允许在 1 月中旬达到债务上限，而没有通过提高上限的法案，因此谈判基本上没有取得任何进展。新上任的众议院议长凯文麦卡锡 (R-CA) 采用了共和党的老策略，即利用违约威胁向民主党同事施压，要求他们接受在正常情况下他们可能不会同意的大幅削减预算。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “看，明年我们不能花更多的钱，”麦卡锡周五在罢工后告诉记者。 “我们必须比前一年花费更少。这很容易。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110469706" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/republicans-press-pause-on-debt-ceiling-talks-as-june-1-default-deadline-looms-1110469706.html?share-block=1110469711" data-title="“Look, we can’t be spending more money next year,” McCarthy told reporters on Friday after the walk-out. “We have to spend less than we spent the year before. It’s pretty easy.”"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">拜登继续坚称，他只会签署一项“干净”的债务上限法案——即在 2024 年预算中没有强制削减预算的法案，这是提高债务上限的典型方式。不过，本周早些时候，拜登和麦卡锡会晤后，两党成员都对达成妥协的可能性持乐观态度。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">国会在第一次世界大战期间设定了债务上限，通过批量而不是零碎地批准来简化拨款过程。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在上个世纪的大部分时间里，它没有任何政治重要性，但在 2011 年，共和党人引入了威胁允许违约的策略，以此作为阻碍平价医疗法案 (ACA) 的一种方式，这是一项广为人知的全面医疗保健法作为奥巴马医改。他们坚持认为联邦政府的预算赤字太大，唯一可以接受的缩减赤字的方法是削减开支，而不是增加税收。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>美国财政部长珍妮特耶伦对即将发生的违约<u><a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/congress-inaction-on-debt-limit-greatest-threat-to-us-economy-since-pandemic---treasury-1110424452.html" target="_blank">发出了可怕的警告</a></u>，违约最早可能在 6 月 1 日发生。周四，她在一次主要银行首席执行官会议上表示，如果政府违约，将产生“严重”的经济后果。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 2011 年，当立法者在账户枯竭前几小时达成协议时，类似情况勉强避免触​​发违约，但标准普尔和穆迪仍因险些失败而下调华盛顿的信用评级。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">拜登目前正在日本参加七国集团峰会，但取消了剩余的亚洲之行，以便返回华盛顿参加债务上限谈判。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 19 May 2023 20:30:08 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/republicans-press-pause-on-debt-ceiling-talks-as-june-1-default-deadline-looms-1110469706.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/republicans-press-pause-on-debt-ceiling-talks-as-june-1-default-deadline-looms-1110469706.html<category>经济</category><category>债务上限</category><category>美国债务上限危机</category><category>共和党人</category><category>凯文麦卡锡</category><category>乔·拜登</category><category>僵局</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[German Defense Minister Wants Special Military Fund Spent Soon to Avoid Inflation Risks]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110469577" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/13/1109673104_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_349079b174caa3efcae39d26d25d09e6.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1109673086" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/german-defense-minister-wants-special-military-fund-spent-soon-to-avoid-inflation-risks-1110469577.html?share-img=1109673086"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Geert Vanden Wijngaert</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">德国国防部长鲍里斯·皮斯托瑞斯 (Boris Pistorius) 于 2023 年 3 月 20 日星期一抵达布鲁塞尔欧洲理事会大楼参加欧盟外交部长和国防部长会议时与媒体交谈。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Germany's Defense Minister Boris Pistorius speaks with the media as he arrives for a meeting of EU foreign and defense ministers at the European Council building in Brussels on Monday, March 20, 2023.  - Sputnik International, 1920, 19.05.2023" title="2023 年 3 月 20 日星期一，德国国防部长鲍里斯·皮斯托瑞斯 (Boris Pistorius) 抵达布鲁塞尔欧洲理事会大楼参加欧盟外交部长和国防部长会议时与媒体交谈。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/13/1109673104_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_5eee2a84b3243ce14fe23bebddebf8ab.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/13/1109673104_0:160:3072:1888_640x0_80_0_0_0e81c7761d93c2b92de3b477533f2d4d.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/13/1109673104_0:160:3072:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_34e9a2cdcd43f0b098cb88c4dc22dcb5.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/13/1109673104_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_5eee2a84b3243ce14fe23bebddebf8ab.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Geert Vanden Wijngaert </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：德国国防部长鲍里斯·皮斯托瑞斯周五表示，他打算尽快动用德国联邦国防军的 1000 亿欧元（1080 亿美元）特别基金，以免其购买力因通货膨胀而降低。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “我将坚持尽快花掉特别基金，以尽可能少地被通货膨胀吞噬。我还打算增加国防部在联邦预算中的份额”他在接受德国媒体采访时说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位部长补充说，在乌克兰持续不断的冲突中，必须重新定义该国武装部队的作用。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">皮斯托瑞斯说：“我们来自和平时期的红利生活，[北约]联盟和国防不那么重要的时代。现在一切都变了，我们必须适应。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110469577" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/german-defense-minister-wants-special-military-fund-spent-soon-to-avoid-inflation-risks-1110469577.html?share-block=1110469580" data-title="&quot;We come from the times when we lived on dividends of the peaceful time and when the [NATO] Alliance and the national defense were less important. Now everything has changed again, and we have to adapt,&quot; Pistorius said.  "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 6月，德国议会和联邦委员会以多数票通过了德国总理奥拉夫·舒尔茨提出的设立1000亿欧元专项基金以提高国家防务能力的倡议，使德军成为欧洲最大的正规军。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 1月27日，皮斯托瑞斯对德国媒体表示，特别国防基金不足以让德国实现军队现代化和支付军事装备的维修费用。随后，有媒体报道称，皮斯托瑞斯曾呼吁德国武装部队的年度预算每年增加100亿欧元。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 19 May 2023 20:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/german-defense-minister-wants-special-military-fund-spent-soon-to-avoid-inflation-risks-1110469577.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/german-defense-minister-wants-special-military-fund-spent-soon-to-avoid-inflation-risks-1110469577.html<category>军队</category><category>鲍里斯·皮斯托瑞斯</category><category>德国</category><category>德国联邦国防军</category><category>通货膨胀</category><category>防御</category><category>运营成本</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Biden Admin Wages Information War Against Americans to Fund Ukraine Conflict]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110469223" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/17/1109779241_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_49e118e38df9d3eef4f6ec6fb067fc98.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1109779082" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/biden-admin-wages-information-war-against-americans-to-fund-ukraine-conflict-1110469223.html?share-img=1109779082"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / LIBKOS</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">Украинские военные с гаубицей M777。 Архивное фото</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Украинские военные с гаубицей M777. Архивное фото - Sputnik International, 1920, 19.05.2023" title="Украинские военные с гаубицей M777。 Архивное фото" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/17/1109779241_0:0:3073:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_7dd3b13fccf72222ef1053bec2d7cf6d.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/17/1109779241_0:0:3073:1728_640x0_80_0_0_cbcd9ef950ed12986e002348f069bf24.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/17/1109779241_0:0:3073:1728_1280x0_80_0_0_90faade0c32f646d294dee7be600bfde.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/17/1109779241_0:0:3073:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_7dd3b13fccf72222ef1053bec2d7cf6d.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / LIBKOS </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">美国向基辅提供的大量军事援助已经引起了美国人的重大担忧，白宫花费数十亿美元资助其针对俄罗斯的代理人战争。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">根据最近的报道，由于五角大楼使用重置成本而不是实际武器成本来对武器进行估价，因此会计错误导致美国高估了运往乌克兰的物资高达 30 亿美元。国防部官员实际上在两个月前就发现了这个问题，但现在才通知国会，这激怒了立法者。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这些报告很容易在<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/biden-deal-with-republicans-over-debt-ceiling-would-reward-hostage-taking-1110461153.html" target="_blank">债务上限陷入僵局</a>之际出现，因为“腾出”数十亿美元让拜登不必向国会要求<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/report-ukraine-has-five-months-to-impress-us-before-being-pressured-into-peace-talks-1110453032.html" target="_blank">为乌克兰军事援助提供额外资金</a>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">但是，这个“小错误”究竟说明了华盛顿的问责制及其在违约迫在眉睫的情况下涉及纳税人资金时的优先事项？</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> EMP 特别工作组学者、前美国国防部官员<strong>戴维·T·派恩 (David T. Pyne)</strong>在接受人造卫星采访时解释了这一令人不安的发现背后的确切原因。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>人造卫星：30亿美元的误算怎么可能？</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>戴维·T·派恩：</strong>鉴于乌克兰报告美国迄今提供了 1960 亿美元的援助，这个数额是乌克兰 2021 年国防预算的 33 倍，而且远远超过其整个 2022 年的国内生产总值，我认为有可能对这个规模做出错误的估计。到目前为止，美国对乌克兰的经济和军事援助几乎没有任何问责制，因为美国国会没有采取任何措施来监督援助的使用情况。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">哥伦比亚广播公司新闻报道称，只有大约 30% 的西方军事援助到达了乌克兰的前线部队，其余大部分援助<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230423/sy-hersh-west-knows-ukraine-weapons-end-up-on-black-market-1109774596.html" target="_blank">都在黑市上出售</a>，以充实包括泽伦斯基总统在内的腐败乌克兰官僚的腰包。报告可能已将高达数亿美元的美国援助收入囊中。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>人造卫星：你认为五角大楼为什么等了两个月才告诉国会？</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>戴维·T·派恩：</strong>我认为我们已经看到拜登政府发表了许多欺骗性言论，旨在欺骗美国人民了解其针对俄罗斯的代理人战争的真相，因为他们知道关于战争起源的难以忽视的真相，事实上，无论<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/us-reportedly-unconvinced-kiev-needs-expensive-f-16s-amid-wests-schism-over-jet-supplies-1110433307.html" target="_blank">美国提供多少军事支持</a>，乌克兰都没有机会赢得它，民众对战争的支持将大大减少。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">因此，五角大楼试图在两个月的时间内向国会隐瞒这一重大会计错误，这一点也不让我感到惊讶。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>人造卫星：这件事有多反常？像这样的误算经常发生吗？这么重大的错误，五角大楼两个月不告诉国会，这正常吗？</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <strong>David T. Pyne：</strong>我自 2005 年以来就没有在国防部工作过，所以我不确定这个会计错误有多正常或有多频繁，但毫无疑问，国会利用这一事件通过法律让美国国防部变得重要是很重要的国防部比现在对国会更加负责，以确保它不会再次发生。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>人造卫星：一名高级国防官员告诉路透社，这一错误“可能会导致更多武器被运往基辅以防御俄罗斯军队。”您是否认为五角大楼有人故意高估了援助，以便向乌克兰运送更多武器？</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <strong>David T. Pyne：</strong>是的，我认为这是很有可能的。拜登政府担心共和党领导的众议院可能不会批准其提议的乌克兰援助计划，因此它可能正在想方设法欺骗国会提供数十亿美元的直接军事援助，根据国防部的说法，目前这一援助已超过 370 亿美元。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">拜登政府的高级官员基本上一直在对美国人民发动信息战、虚假信息和观念管理运动，以让他们<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/russian-strike-eliminates-massive-stock-of-foreign-weapons-and-ammo-in-ukraine-1110442643.html" target="_blank">支持乌克兰的战争</a>，这场战争是为了反对美国的国家安全利益而进行的。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">话虽如此，我确实认为，在整个历史上，世界各国政府宣传其公民支持损害自身利益的战争是非常普遍的，因此拜登政府的欺骗性战争宣传活动在这方面并不是独一无二的。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>俄罗斯卫星通讯社：您认为这一事件对未来对乌克兰的供应有什么影响吗？您是否希望五角大楼的人员下次在处理数字时更加严格？</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>戴维·T·派恩：</strong>我希望这一事件能让国会议员暂停向乌克兰提供任何额外援助，直到我们迄今为止向他们提供的援助完全负责为止。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">然而，鉴于民主党仍然控制着美国参议院，而且许多众议院共和党高层仍然支持单方面解除美国军队的武装，以便向乌克兰运送数千个更先进的武器系统，我怀疑它是否会这样做。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 19 May 2023 18:17:04 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/biden-admin-wages-information-war-against-americans-to-fund-ukraine-conflict-1110469223.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/biden-admin-wages-information-war-against-americans-to-fund-ukraine-conflict-1110469223.html<category>分析</category><category>我们</category><category>乌克兰危机</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>军事援助</category><category>美国军事援助</category><category>五角大楼</category></item></channel></rss>